Table: Applicability
Filter rows: fx → concat('_pei_controlprocedure_value eq ', first(outputs('Find_Removed_CP_Record')?['body/value'])?['pei_controlprocedureid'], ' and pei_applicabilitystatus eq 890920000')
Rename to: List Applicability For Removed CP
